OL,3,CUpdate on when boil water notice could
OL,4,Cbe fully lifted in Brixham
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News West
OL,7,FCountry on Sunday 19 May, incident
OL,8,Fdirector David Harris said: "We will
OL,9,Flift the boil water notice in the
OL,10,FHillhead area as soon as we can in
OL,11,Fagreement with our public health
OL,12,Fpartners.
OL,14,F"We have to flush our network of
OL,15,Fcryptosporidium and then get a series
OL,16,Fof clear test results.
OL,18,F"We are looking to mid to late next
OL,19,Fweek before we can lift the boil water
OL,20,Fnotice in Hillhead."
