OL,3,CUpdate on when boil water notice could
OL,4,Cbe fully lifted in Brixham
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency has so
OL,7,Ffar confirmed 46 cases of the parasite
OL,8,F- but more than 100 other people have
OL,9,Freported similar symptoms.
OL,11,FAround 17,000 households were told to
OL,12,Fboil any water they consumed from
OL,13,FWednesday 15 May onwards.
OL,15,FOn Saturday 18 May, that notice was
OL,16,Flifted from the Alston network area -
OL,17,Faround 14,000 homes - but remains in
OL,18,Fplace for 2,500 households in the
OL,19,FHillhead, upper Brixham and Kingswear
OL,20,Fareas.
