OL,3,CUpdate on when boil water notice could
OL,4,Cbe fully lifted in Brixham
OL,6,FExtra compensation for people in
OL,7,FHillhead, upper Brixham and Kingswear
OL,9,FSouth West Water has promised an extra
OL,10,F#100 compensation to customers who are
OL,11,Fstill under a boil water notice in
OL,12,FBrixham.
OL,14,FAll of those affected were initially
OL,15,Ftold they would get #15, but this rose
OL,16,Fto #100 shortly afterwards.
OL,18,FNow, anyone living in Hillhead, upper
OL,19,FBrixham and Kingswear, is entitled to
OL,20,F#215 total compensation.
