OL,3,CUpdate on when boil water notice could
OL,4,Cbe fully lifted in Brixham
OL,6,FSouth West Water said that equated to
OL,7,Fnearly half the average annual water
OL,8,Fbill.
OL,10,FWhere did the parasite come from?
OL,12,FSouth West Water said in a statement
OL,13,Fon Sunday 19 May: "We have already
OL,14,Fidentified a probable cause at
OL,15,FHillhead - a damaged air valve on
OL,16,Fprivate farmland - and are urgently
OL,17,Finvestigating how this happened."
OL,19,FEarlier this week, it was suggested
OL,20,Fthat the parasite itself could have
OL,21,Fcome from cow manure on the farmland.
