OL,6,FThe statement continued: "The Hillhead
OL,7,Freservoir has been successfully
OL,8,Fdrained, thoroughly cleaned, and we
OL,9,Fwill start refilling today.
OL,11,F"We will also start flushing the wider
OL,12,FHillhead network today, which is being
OL,13,Fcontinuously monitored as we work to
OL,14,Feliminate any traces of
OL,15,Fcryptosporidium."
