OL,3,CUpdate on when boil water notice could
OL,4,Cbe fully lifted in Brixham
OL,6,FMr Harris said: "Very pleasingly,
OL,7,Ftoday the crypto tests show no
OL,8,Fcryptosporidium in the Hillhead
OL,9,Freservoir.
OL,11,F"There is still crypto in the Hillhead
OL,12,Fnetwork but it's very encouraging for
OL,13,Fus to see that as the water flows
OL,14,Fthrough the system, those crypto
OL,15,Fresults are coming in showing no
OL,16,Fcrypto in that storage reservoir."
